author: The Critical Drinker
description: Has Marvel finally managed to redeem themselves with a good Daredevil show? Did we just see the most boring Oscars ever? And could things get any worse for Snow White? Join me, MauLer, Platoon and Movie Cynic to find out.
title: Open Bar #133 - Daredevil Born Again? Oscars Flop, Snow White Box Office Predictions
